column1: As a Marketing Manager and Growth Strategist with a decade of experience, I've spent nearly seven years honing my skills in Digital Marketing. As a Digital Marketing Manager, I've crafted over 100 long-term Marketing Strategies and brought to life more than 100 projects with a budget of $1.000.000 in the USA and European markets. My qualifications come from the Top-Ranked universities, including Trinity College Dublin (Ireland), The Chartered Institute of Marketing (UK), Digital Marketing Institute (Ireland), and Wharton University (USA). I'm excited to continue utilizing my expertise to help businesses achieve their marketing goals.
üåü I have a work permit in the Netherlands through Highly Educated Persona Visa.
